Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.79,0:01:44.71,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.59,0:01:48.75,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.29,0:01:50.84,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,We've been given permission.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.09,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,Let's go in.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.01,0:01:57.80,Alt,Yo,0,0,0,,Come on, what's Nai-chan's condition?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.26,Alt,Yo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tell me, Gramps!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.64,0:02:00.26,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun, keep down.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.60,0:02:01.77,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.60,0:02:01.77,Alt,Gr,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hold your tongue!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.44,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Moron, you're being too loud around the patient!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.24,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,There are no injuries on his body,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.24,0:02:14.74,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,but for a moment there was a strong disturbance in his brain waves.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.49,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Now he has temporarily lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.49,0:02:20.49,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,You should probably investigate the reason behind this at the Research Tower.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.74,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.74,0:02:25.96,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Then, I shall not waste any more time and will take my leave immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.67,0:02:29.75,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Take that fool over there with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.88,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Feel free to use him for human experimentation.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.59,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,Doc, when will he regain consciousness?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.51,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,I'm responsible...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.47,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,I was entrusted to look after him and yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.14,0:02:45.98,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,His condition is stable, so I think he should wake up soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.60,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Tsukumo, you should learn to relax more.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.94,0:02:56.78,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,You only need to shoulder your own responsibilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.87,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,I'll take my leave now!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.16,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,Please, take care of Nai-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.37,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.50,Default,Creatures,0,0,0,,Ma~ Ma~ Ma~ Ma~
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.13,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,He was in so much pain before,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.71,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,and yet you say there's nothing wrong with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.25,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You're not some kind of quack, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.55,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,You're such a foul-mouthed kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.05,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Worried about your friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.43,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,We just happened to be together.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.43,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous to assume that we're friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.89,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Encounters happen both through coincidence and through the course of nature.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.65,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,If trust grows from within here,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.19,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,you'll be friends forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.66,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.45,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Supper! I'm going for supper!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.95,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Make sure you look after him!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.20,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.33,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nai.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.58,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why aren't you devoting all your attention to finding me?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.00,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there someone by your side?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.01,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku!{*}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.97,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.31,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}What kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.73,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Oh, Gareki...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.77,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be able to make friends with someone...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.23,0:04:15.02,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}that's my boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.15,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...  let's say goodbye to that person.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.03,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.40,Default,Na,0,0,0,,But... why?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.78,0:04:27.08,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, because I don't want you to feel sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.91,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should tell him, "Gareki, I don't need you!"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.33,Default,Na,0,0,0,,But I... Gareki is...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.42,0:04:40.67,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}You wouldn't want him to be dragged into the scary things happening around you,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.97,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}and be broken, would you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.64,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Ga–
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.32,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You startled me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.65,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.66,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,If there's anything you want me to do, I'll hear you out this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.62,0:05:06.41,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Ga–
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.66,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}You wouldn't want him to be broken, would you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.96,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Gareki, I don't need you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.96,0:05:16.83,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.67,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Gareki, I don't...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.34,0:05:22.67,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Tell me... what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.88,0:05:23.72,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.43,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Gareki's sca–{note from TL:in JP, Nai pauses at "kowa"(kowasu - break), but next line Gareki misunderstand him as saying "kowai"(scary), so I'm leaving this interrupted at "sca"(scattered ->break)}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.43,0:05:30.77,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I'm scary? You're saying this after all we've been through?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.90,0:05:34.43,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Ga–
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.15,0:05:38.36,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Gareki!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.44,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.20,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Are you telling me that you'll give me what I want, so I should just go away?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.75,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Since you're already acquainted with Circus...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.87,0:05:56.21,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I hate people who act innocent but are actually opportunists.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.57,0:06:24.24,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.24,0:06:28.03,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Geez... Gramps, you're no ordinary old man,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.83,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,so go easy on me– Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.83,0:06:30.66,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.16,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.16,0:06:33.83,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.83,Default,Nai,0,0,0,,Tell that bearded old geezer that the damn brat is awake!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.83,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I get it... so just calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.71,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,All right? Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.71,0:06:42.54,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Wai–
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.55,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.71,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.47,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.31,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.39,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Where does it hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.90,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Um... what should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.86,0:07:01.02,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Tsukumo-chan... huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.44,0:07:06.82,Alt,Creatures,0,0,0,,{\an8}Off-limits! Off-limits! Off-limits!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.61,0:07:02.28,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yogi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.15,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.32,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yogi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.40,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yogi!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.78,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.37,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.37,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Tsukumo, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.95,0:07:18.54,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,So? You didn't come here for supper, did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.13,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,About that boy's body...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.67,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Nai's body?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.97,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Are there any significant problems with it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.68,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Well... to put it simply,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.81,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,that boy isn't human.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.18,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,He's an animal.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.06,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,It's natural that you'd feel shocked–
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.69,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,What a bad joke... oh no it's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.57,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,I heard that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.07,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Here! Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.82,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,This is the true form of that boy!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.62,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.45,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.25,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,I've come to this conclusion based on cellular tissue samples extracted from his body.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.71,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Its scientific name is "Niji."
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.05,0:08:08.59,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,Its species can only be found in the Niji Forest, which contains a unique ecosystem.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.72,Default,Gr,0,0,0,,It's an extremely rare animal.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.72,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.93,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Wait, wait a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.35,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,But if what Doc says is true...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.35,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.15,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does he expect me to believe that Nai's not actually human...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.86,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}That based on the data, he's an animal...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.36,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I can simply accept all this!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.61,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since meeting members of Circus,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.20,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\i1}I've learned that there are humans who become monsters.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.16,0:08:37.66,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though it's true that Nai's actions always tend to be a bit strange...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.33,0:08:41.17,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does this mean that up until now...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.09,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Gareki.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.29,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.29,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nai!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.38,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.30,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come again?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.55,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}You saved me again!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.51,0:08:58.05,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\i1}Gareki, I don't need you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.31,0:08:58.05,Alt,Na,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\i1}Don't need you! Don't need you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.10,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been such a fool?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.77,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I've talked to the Research Tower.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.32,0:09:09.94,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Bring him there tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.94,0:09:13.44,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Urp... I'm going to see Akari-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.44,0:09:16.70,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Oh... that reminds me, about Nai-chan's bracelet,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.62,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,you're not going to take it from him?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.12,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to see if it responds to that boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.08,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.58,0:09:27.42,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,But wouldn't the bracelet only respond to its owner?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.26,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Nai-chan said it was left by that guy, Karoku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.34,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,What if he's lying?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.96,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.97,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,If he's a member of Kafka, it would be possible, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.35,0:09:37.47,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.89,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I was surprised to find out about his body...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.47,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,but I'm sure he's a good boy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.94,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Wai– What are you laughing about?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.94,0:09:46.85,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Oh nothing...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.48,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,That's why I assigned you to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.90,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,You're probably thinking that I'll definitely go easy on him...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.24,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Don't think too much about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.15,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,All these little safeguards are just a precaution.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.78,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.13,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.13,0:10:12.42,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's just a boy... no, just an animal.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.80,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how you look at it, he looks like a human...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.30,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now they're saying that he's an animal?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.93,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}That just makes me even more embarrassed!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.56,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I'll look like a fool if I get angry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.56,0:10:27.81,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,In fact, you've always asked me for help, so what's this about me being scary?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.07,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Talk to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.06,Default,Nai,0,0,0,,You're not scary!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.23,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.57,0:10:37.99,Default,Na,0,0,0,,I was told that you would be broken... by Karoku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.74,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Karoku?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.95,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.25,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.71,Default,Na,0,0,0,,If I don't want you getting dragged into the scary things, and being broken...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.71,0:10:52.54,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku said I should say goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.51,Default,Na,0,0,0,,He said it would be better if I told you that I didn't need you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.13,0:11:00.22,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,How can you speak to a person you can't even find?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.72,0:11:01.97,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Just now...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.72,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Before I woke up...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.40,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's trying to tell me... that it happened in a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.73,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn animal!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.61,0:11:13.57,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said I should say goodbye to avoid you being broken.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.57,0:11:16.53,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said it would be better if I said I didn't need you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.53,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I think about it, what a {\i0}"great"{\i1} personality that guy has.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.24,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}He seems like a hypocrite...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.96,0:11:29.37,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I'll ask again. What's your relationship with Karoku?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.54,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku's always been with me–
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.88,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You've already said that!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.09,0:11:36.51,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,So, how long have you been so close?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.72,Default,Na,0,0,0,,As long as I remember...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.13,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Roughly when?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.06,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't know?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.97,0:11:48.39,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Well then, did you tell Karoku about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.27,Default,Na,0,0,0,,I told him I was with you...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.98,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that all?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.98,0:11:56.57,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, why did Karoku try to keep me away from him?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.57,0:12:00.40,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those words even seem to have malicious intent.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.40,0:12:04.70,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also if he can communicate, why did he leave this boy alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.41,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact, how is he communicating.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.21,0:12:13.87,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's how he sets off communication, he really does have some {\i0}"great"{\i1} taste.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.17,0:12:21.89,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, my impression of you has changed quite a bit, Karoku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.64,0:12:27.93,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}On top of that, he's picking a fight with me...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.15,0:12:32.23,Default,NA,0,0,0,,Gareki?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.98,0:12:37.94,Default,GA,0,0,0,,First of all; I'm sorry, I heard you wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.57,Default,GA,0,0,0,,I don't really dislike you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.33,Default,GA,0,0,0,,Moreover,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.08,Default,GA,0,0,0,,I have no intention of being broken.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.34,Default,GA,0,0,0,,I've also taken interest in meeting Karoku
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.75,Default,NA,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.97,Default,HI,0,0,0,,From now on, you will be examined in the Research Tower.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.35,0:13:08.47,Default,GA,0,0,0,,If it's about Nai being an animal and not being human,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.60,Default,GA,0,0,0,,he won't be treated like a lab animal, will he?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.52,Default,HI,0,0,0,,Doc will go with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.65,Default,HI,0,0,0,,If they try to use Nai for any experiments, scream and beg him to help.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.65,0:13:17.86,Default,YO,0,0,0,,What kind of advice is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.86,0:13:18.73,Default,HI,0,0,0,,Yogi,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.48,Default,HI,0,0,0,,I will leave these two in your care.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.90,0:13:25.37,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Yes, but what about Hirato-san and Tsukumo-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.61,Default,KI,0,0,0,,We're being called to Round Table Z?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.12,0:13:33.37,Default,KI,0,0,0,,Why didn't they take them to the Research Tower right away?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.37,0:13:37.88,Default,JI,0,0,0,,I think their reason for being cautious is to find out who the real owner of that bracelet is.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.30,Default,KI,0,0,0,,Their methods are messed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.38,Default,TS,0,0,0,,We'll find out when we get there.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.55,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Fly... high!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.02,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Yahooo!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.27,Default,KI,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsukumo-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.53,Default,KI,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.53,0:14:02.95,Default,KI,0,0,0,,Did you gain a little weight?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.82,Default,JI,0,0,0,,Now now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.03,0:14:13.54,Default,TS,0,0,0,,Those companies that cooperate with Kafka are not only good at hiding their association,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.54,0:14:17.66,Default,TS,0,0,0,,but the number of Varuga which had decreased at one point are starting to increase again.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.21,0:14:24.80,Default,MA,0,0,0,,They stole the evolution research we had sealed, and are using it as we speak.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.43,0:14:30.05,Default,MA,0,0,0,,We have to protect many lives from the mistakes of our former comrades.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.98,Default,MA,0,0,0,,And, Hirato.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.98,0:14:35.52,Default,MA,0,0,0,,About the boy that Doc has reported on...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.11,0:14:42.06,Default,RY,0,0,0,,There is nothing physically wrong with you, including your blood cells.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.57,Default,RY,0,0,0,,Everything is fine, except for your personality.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.07,Default,GA,0,0,0,,Then, I'll take these off.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.12,Default,RY,0,0,0,,Thank you for your trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.74,Default,RY,0,0,0,,We have a room ready for you. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.45,Default,RY,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, where is Yogi?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.00,Default,GA,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.96,Default,GA,0,0,0,,He left before I noticed.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.96,0:15:03.34,Alt,RY,0,0,0,,Well, I thought he was already getting prodded, he's such a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.21,Default,YO,0,0,0,,No one else is around.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.34,Default,YO,0,0,0,,He's not around...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.05,Default,AK,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.55,Default,YO,0,0,0,,What! Ah, Akari-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.05,Default,AK,0,0,0,,Are you changing your bandage every day?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.05,0:15:12.43,Default,AK,0,0,0,,The reaction can be terrifying, if you don't take it seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.35,0:15:18.23,Default,AK,0,0,0,,If you forget it again, treatment would not be as easy as the last time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.23,0:15:25.36,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Well, I.. I.. will try my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.17,Default,NA,0,0,0,,It looks a lot like where I lived with Karoku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.46,Default,GA,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.41,Default,NA,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.75,Default,NA,0,0,0,,What was the place Gareki lived like?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.39,0:15:52.47,Default,GA,0,0,0,,It was a filthy dump.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.39,0:16:02.19,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you're in a dirty place with dirty people, you don't forget the anger towards them.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.19,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.81,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't forgotten
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.78,0:16:07.65,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.78,0:16:13.82,Default,GA,0,0,0,,Since I met you, I feel like I only see pure things.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.33,0:16:18.54,Default,GA,0,0,0,,Seeing so many things and learning how to think purely,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.83,Default,GA,0,0,0,,then growing up and forgetting the anger.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.83,Default,GA,0,0,0,,I don't want to be the only one who is comfortable.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.51,0:16:30.09,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if, unconsciously, I wanted to escape...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.09,0:16:34.22,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}If being with Nai prevents me from running away.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.35,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I go back?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.35,Default,NA,0,0,0,,Gareki.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.31,Default,NA,0,0,0,,If you can see pure things as pure,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.73,Default,NA,0,0,0,,that means Gareki's eyes are pure too!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.74,Default,NA,0,0,0,,Gareki, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.45,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.78,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was pretty pissed off.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.49,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\i1}I {\i0}am{\i1} still filthy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.92,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,Gareki...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.22,0:17:14.26,Default,AK,0,0,0,,His internal body formation is quite similar to a Varuga,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.26,0:17:17.98,Default,AK,0,0,0,,but Nai is a new species formed from the miraculous...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.85,Default,AK,0,0,0,,co-existence and amalgamation of human and Niji cells.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.31,0:17:26.10,Default,AK,0,0,0,,The one who created Nai is undoubtedly a genius.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.69,0:17:30.48,Default,MA,0,0,0,,Then, dissect him immediately to unravel the details.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.53,0:17:32.40,Default,HI,0,0,0,,Tsukumo,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.57,Default,HI,0,0,0,,sit down.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.91,Default,AK,0,0,0,,I cannot follow that order.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.91,0:17:38.91,Default,MA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.91,0:17:42.66,Default,AK,0,0,0,,If we dissect him, we will lose an enormous amount of invaluable data.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.08,0:17:47.21,Default,AK,0,0,0,,I cannot accept throwing away such a masterpiece without any consideration.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.64,Default,YO,0,0,0,,They are from Doc.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.92,Default,NA,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.47,Default,GA,0,0,0,,Treating you like a pet...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.56,Default,GA,0,0,0,,Aren't you just being used?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.43,Default,YO,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.44,0:18:06.81,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Nai-chan offered to come with us of his own accord.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.19,Default,NA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Niji Forest?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.19,0:18:12.74,Default,RY,0,0,0,,{\i1}The place we think you were living.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.74,0:18:15.94,Default,YO,0,0,0,,{\i1}We may find something out if we go there.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.58,Default,YO,0,0,0,,{\i1}About both Nai-chan and Karoku-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.70,Default,RY,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you don't wish to cooperate with us and would rather leave instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make sure I "sleep soundly" tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.46,Default,NA,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will go.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.55,0:18:31.97,Default,NA,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to truly understand what Karoku meant.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.97,0:18:39.09,Default,NA,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\i1}I also want to have a better understanding of what everyone is thinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.14,Default,YO,0,0,0,,You're such a good boy, Nai-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.81,Default,GA,0,0,0,,You're annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.47,Default,GA,0,0,0,,Hurry up and take off already!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.48,0:18:50.28,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Then, we'll be blasting off toward Niji Forest!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.94,Alt,AK,0,0,0,,Blast off? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.20,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Sorry, well, we're taking off.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.15,0:19:04.41,Default,AK,0,0,0,,Niji Forest is a peculiar area where unnatural rainbows and mirages occur.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.41,0:19:08.83,Default,AK,0,0,0,,Its unique ecological electromagnetic waves influence the optical nerve.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.33,0:19:13.09,Default,AK,0,0,0,,This electromagnetic wave causes all electronic devices to malfunction.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.59,0:19:18.10,Default,AK,0,0,0,,So, this leads to a search that can only depend on hearing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.10,0:19:23.60,Default,GA,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\i1}So that's why Nai, being an animal from that place, is so sensitive to sound...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.91,Default,AK,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been about an hour.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.91,0:19:41.95,Default,AK,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is walking without hesitation, where there is no distinct trail.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.00,Default,AK,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that a mirage?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.96,Default,AK,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.86,Default,AK,0,0,0,,Only the house is burnt.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.44,0:20:16.95,Default,AK,0,0,0,,The destruction wasn't due to natural causes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.95,0:20:17.82,Default,AK,0,0,0,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.03,Default,WO & MA,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.03,Alt,WO & MA,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.87,Default,AK,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was seen in the aerial photos of the forest.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.54,0:20:28.37,Default,AK,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would have been impossible to reach without Nai.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.37,0:20:32.46,Default,AK,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some unnatural being came to erase the evidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.80,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Nai-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.26,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.88,Default,NA,0,0,0,,There is another place I stayed for a long time.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.09,Default,AK,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.10,Default,NA,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.60,Default,GA,0,0,0,,A cave?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.69,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.69,0:20:53.60,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.06,Default,AK,0,0,0,,Varuga?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.95,0:21:04.83,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Are you after Nai-chan again?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.45,0:21:09.91,Default,YO,0,0,0,,I'm actually scared of fighting since failure isn't an option.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.37,0:21:12.54,Default,YO,0,0,0,,But I will fight if I need to fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.06,0:21:31.81,Default,GA,0,0,0,,Nai!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.19,Default,YO,0,0,0,,Damn it!
